6 SECTION 2. APPROPRIATION - BANK OF NORTH DAKOTA - EDUCATION SAVINGS
7 ACCOUNT PROGRAM. There is appropriated out of any moneys in the general fund in the
8 state treasury, not otherwise appropriated, the sum of $40,000,000, or so much of the sum as
9 may be necessary, to the Bank of North Dakota for the purpose of funding the education
